Name: Swift Action
Desc: <color=#0F70BC>Bonus:</color> Action Point +1. Criticism can further reduce the Master's level by 1 in this round\n\nI want all members to contain this crisis as fast as possible. No matter how it started, it cannot keep going this way. —Member of Parliament

Name: Every Second Counts
Desc: <color=#0F70BC>Bonus:</color> Movement costs no Action Points in this round\n\nBetter finish the rest of the mission fast before the situation gets out of control. —Vera

Name: Anxious Exploration
Desc: <color=#0F70BC>Bonus:</color> Criticism can further reduce the Master's level by 2 in this round. All Master Level +1 in the next round\n\nThe spreading anxiety has turned hands into claws.

Name: Uneasy Situation
Desc: <color=#0F70BC>Bonus:</color> Movement costs no Action Points in this round\n\nThe Parliament has come to a conclusion. As the situation worsens, the hawks are forced to launch a quick assault before things get completely out of control. —Member of Parliament

Name: Intelligence Priority
Desc: <color=#0F70BC>Bonus:</color> Action Points +2. Quantity of Paint obtained in this round +1\n\nTry to obtain as much intelligence as possible before taking an action. —Lee

Name: Customization Assistant
Desc: <color=#0F70BC>Bonus:</color> Action Points +5. Quantity of Three-Color Paint +5\n\nAnalysis of all art Schools complete. Auto-painting system loaded and running. —Lee

Name: First Battle
Desc: <color=#0F70BC>Bonus:</color> Action Points +2. Quantity of Paint obtained in this round +2\n\nA new School must prove their worth to other awakened machines, at least from an artistic perspective.

Name: Expanding Influence
Desc: <color=#0F70BC>Bonus:</color> Action Points +5. Quantity of Three-Color Paint +5\n\nIt's our turn now to think about how to expand the influence of our school. Perhaps increasing production would be a good idea. —Lee

Name: Fantasy Affinity
Desc: <color=#0F70BC>Bonus:</color> Blue Master Level +1, Red/Green Master Level -1 in the next round\n\nHmm... Somehow, I feel that Fantastical Mechanical Impressionism would suit me better. —Ayla

Name: Bridge of Art
Desc: <color=#0F70BC>Bonus:</color> Action Points +5. Upgrading Exhibition only costs 5 Paint in this round \n\nSometimes, art is like a bridge. It can break the language barrier and convey your emotions to another person. —Ayla

Name: Art Catalysis
Desc: <color=#0F70BC>Bonus:</color> Quantity of Three-Color Paint +4. All Master Level +1 in the next round\n\nAyla's effort did not reduce the mechanoids' passion in fighting each other. In contrast, the most obsessive ones have become even more passionate.

Name: Bridge of Art
Desc: <color=#0F70BC>Bonus:</color> Action Points +5. Upgrading Exhibition only costs 5 Paint in this round \n\nSometimes, art is like a bridge. It can break the language barrier and convey your emotions to another person. —Ayla

Name: Thorough Planning
Desc: <color=#0F70BC>Bonus:</color> Quantity of Paint obtained in this round +1. Able to reroll 2 times\n\nUnlike that stubborn fool, I am flawless and so is my plan. —Teddy

Name: Swift Decision
Desc: <color=#0F70BC>Bonus:</color> Action Points +5. Guaranteed to obtain the maximum quantity of Paint in this round \n\nUnlike that hesitant fool, I'm all brave and bold, and now is the time to charge forward. —Karenina

Name: Backup Plan
Desc: <color=#0F70BC>Bonus:</color> Quantity of Three-Color Paint +3. Able to reroll 3 times in this round.\n\nThere are four proposals on the table, preparing against all sorts of emergency situations.

Name: Proactive Action
Desc: <color=#0F70BC>Bonus:</color> Action Points +5. Guaranteed to obtain the maximum quantity of Paint in this round\n\nCompared with the consequence of missing the best opportunity, a little recklessness is acceptable.

Desc: <color=#0F70BC>Bonus:</color> Green Master Level -1. Movement in Green area costs no Action Points in this round\n\nA proposal that suggests to let the admins determine the outcome of this contest has won the support of some members within the School.

Desc: <color=#0F70BC>Bonus:</color> Quantity of Green Paint -5. Timeline events are not tallied in this round\n\nThe admin position was created by Cervantes himself. This title has earned a certain level of trust from the awakened machines.
